msgid ""
"If the number of defective items out of %1$d sampled is <= %2$d, accept the "
"lot. Reject otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Si el número de elementos defectuosos de %1$d muestreados es <= %2$d, acepta "
"el lote. Recházalo en caso contrario."

msgid "Create Variable Plan"
msgstr "Crear Plan de Variables"

msgid ""
"Z.LSL = (mean - LSL) / historical standard deviation\n"
"\n"
"Accept lot if Z.LSL >= k, otherwise reject."
msgstr ""
"Z.LSL = (media - LSL) / desviación estándar histórica\n"
"\n"
"Acepta el lote si Z.LSL >= k; de lo contrario, rechazar."

msgid ""
"Variable plan generated for the current quality constraints is invalid. "
"Modify the quality constraints."
msgstr ""
"El plan de variables generado para las restricciones de calidad vigentes, no "
"es válido. Modifica las restricciones de calidad."

msgid ""
"Variable plan generated for the current quality constraints has an invalid "
